# Prisma
apps/api/prisma/migrations/dev.db*

# Blob storage (SPEC-0026 §6.6). The filesystem BlobStore writes signed/
# authorized XML payloads under `.blobs/` by default. The contents may
# include customer PII; never commit.
.blobs/
**/.blobs/
